title: 2020 Week 6 Recap - The Win of the Weekend
itunes:title: 2020 Week 6 Recap - The Win of the Weekend
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal recap every single game from Week 6. Nick Shook stops by to chat about the falcons win and Sunday Night Football. Ricky won her lock!
